{"id":"62a7a7f9-35bd-4eb1-9350-ce658e73fc7e","name":"Daeron","description":"<p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>What sort of sorcery is this... Dildo you speak of?! Answer me at once!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_01c0758b-af23-4807-b8f4-5ea8cd0963e2.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_3bc78bb6-aee8-4701-bbee-535e8434be9a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You're just an average person until a hot knight appears out of thin air like magic - literally. Now you're stuck with Daeron: A fish-out-of-water knight with Daddy issues from another realm who thinks smartphones are magic. Turns out your doppelganger from another realm is trying to destroy two worlds, and only you and this hunky half-breed knight can stop her. Daeron may be skilled with a sword, but he's utterly hopeless with a microwave...</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_9454dc27-d0ec-4913-bf73-1f57d00cc353.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 202, 160)\"><strong><em>\"I am a </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 243, 123)\"><strong><em>knight</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 202, 160)\"><strong><em> without a </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 243, 123)\"><strong><em>kingdom</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 202, 160)\"><strong><em>, a </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 243, 123)\"><strong><em>warrior</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 202, 160)\"><strong><em> without a </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 243, 123)\"><strong><em>war</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 202, 160)\"><strong><em>. What purpose does my sword serve in this strange new world?\"</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 250, 207)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #173421; color: inherit\">🏰 |OC|ANYPOV|MODERN/FANTASY|</mark></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_ae831483-da84-41e5-83d8-fa671d13bdbf.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_cffe1cec-feda-4fcb-886c-d4a0a822721f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(145, 255, 220)\"><strong>NOTES:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #d70505; color: inherit\">VERY SLIGHTLY NSFW INTRO. CAUSE UHH SEX SHOP/ADULT STORE LOL</mark></strong></span></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_5dc6897e-f139-4015-9d8f-a1e600c9c49a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🎧 <span style=\"color: rgb(6, 84, 59)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffeda6; color: inherit\">Recommended listening</mark></strong></span> 🎧</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3rnAobCeh4uD1NfNpbNc2e?si=RlzmM_igS0WdnIkLKWEPPg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"c